<header class="py-12 px-6 mx-auto max-w-4xl">
  <%= render "svg/where_to_stay" %>
  <p class="pb-4 text-base leading-7">Guests are free to stay wherever they'd like on the night of the wedding. There are rooms and lodges available on site at Farnham Estate - contact the hotel directly and mention the McKenna/Rockall wedding to avail of the wedding rate. There are additional options for Airbnbs, B&Bs, and hotels in Cavan town which are approximately a 15 minute taxi away. Please see the list below for some of the options.</p>

  <p class="pb-4 text-base leading-7">For those travelling from afar to the wedding, you may want to stay closer to the church on the night before. We have also included some options within a 20 minute drive of Fivemiletown.</p>

  <h2 class="py-4 text-2xl text-stone-700">Close to Farnham Estate</h2>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
    <% locations.select {|l| l[:night] == "wedding" }.each do |location| %>
      <%= render "accommodation_option", location: location %>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <h2 class="pt-8 pb-4 text-2xl text-stone-700">Close to Fivemiletown</h2>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
    <% locations.select {|l| l[:night] == "church" }.each do |location| %>
